{"tid":2249694,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"超時空要塞Delta啲歌咁好聽動物台竟然冇人講？？","createTime":"2020-10-19T13:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T10:08:26.000Z","uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"61e4718e7a0ff0a469bbd0742e2c8bde1a17dec6","tid":2249694,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RV3k0uj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRV3k0uj.jpg&h=b91a1e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一集首神洗腦當年熱門到成個動漫界都知，之後每集都唱下靚歌，首首都好有heart好高質<br />\n<br />\n劇情峰迴路轉之餘，人物描寫得好好，由女主乜都唔識成長到拯救銀河嘅歌姬，梅沙嘅壯烈故事又做得好好，仲要同嗰集首歌好夾<br />\n<br />\n到結尾局中局中局又合理解釋到，同時維持到超時空要塞系列一貫高潮位男女主告白傳統同三角戀<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係劇中啲歌係配動畫即時唱，差唔多等於要1take過，但仍然可以保持甚至好過專輯水準<br />\n<br />\n咁高質點解完全冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b10b7ea6b2cb33c83a4a231e964021dbb419c9","tid":2249694,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a0f18acf5c60f6df27d60a2eb37ffe3f41bd0a","tid":2249694,"uid":228894,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qCpi2l8i07g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqCpi2l8i07g&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=2ad28095\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qCpi2l8i07g</a>"},{"pid":"8d73208aea5f16f35bd6647610f4e977a4893c91","tid":2249694,"uid":258809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:31:04.000Z","msg":"推, 同意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc3acc54a1ca5012637398cd6da6de35a37d075","tid":2249694,"uid":47475,"like":2